snippet.title: Fix Me Up Doc! – Dark Humor - PC Playthrough (Steam)
snippet.description:
Formerly known as "Super Sports Surgery"

A sausage on his left hand and ketchup on the right – a simulator of the most difficult profession in the world, that's surgery! But this isn't just a simple medical game with crazy operations.

This is a parody game with dark humor, with such unbelievable graphics and so intense levels that you can even feel the smell.

Fix Me Up Doc! – Dark Humor (C) Atomic Fabrik
Developed and Published by Gamesforfarm / Atomic Fabrik / Cristian Manolachi
